{"tid":1456051,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"不要說前線決定","createTime":"2019-08-12T09:40:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-12T10:03:21.000Z","uid":84040,"like":12,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"09b9d16fada68ca53f429ce8350f9690df691bf2","tid":1456051,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:40:19.000Z","msg":"試著說<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: red;\">自己決定</span></strong></span><br />\n大家都知前線周圍都係鬼<br />\n你走唔走係你自己既決定<br />\n唔好俾人影響<br />\n唔好人地話留你就留<br />\n唔好人地話走你就走<br />\n唔好因為見有人留就陪佢留<br />\n唔好見有人走就齊齊走<br />\n每個人都係獨立既個體<br />\n可能聆聽意見<br />\n但一定要自己分析<br />\n咁先係流水社運既精髓"},{"pid":"056aca0afa06d829d92c3df1aab787a4b803ed4a","tid":1456051,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:40:28.000Z","msg":"1"},{"pid":"11ca990ce6ecd7e1380a8496ccfab0832653c81b","tid":1456051,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:40:38.000Z","msg":"2"},{"pid":"7e4d36f02d864d410c773dc32b7f8f74997f2499","tid":1456051,"uid":13663,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:40:52.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">勇武巴打門 今日黑警既目標100%係你地 千千千萬要忍下手<br />\n<br />\n市區都唔好去</span></span>"},{"pid":"d74337564ed2884114cffbd86dae8fe39b7a5d5e","tid":1456051,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:41:35.000Z","msg":"3"},{"pid":"32cf8359c3b0b6dbe3442cc375f3e6f5b24c2aab","tid":1456051,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:41:59.000Z","msg":"負皮我既就留言"},{"pid":"1d9de01cab1a7d90f87912db6fd38a619fef677b","tid":1456051,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:42:14.000Z","msg":"唔好偷偷留下負評"},{"pid":"274580025d3d4c1d460fcd78c25a41b13da4fa37","tid":1456051,"uid":84040,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-12T09:42:25.000Z","msg":"4"},{"pid":"2392a0ff7980